Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.57,0:00:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey there, my\Nunicorn friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.51,0:00:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you heard?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.58,0:00:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,About Princess Twilight\NSparkle's coronation?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.88,0:00:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Who hasn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.88,0:00:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm on my way there now. So\Nmuch baking to do and...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.41,0:00:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, about the\NEarth ponies.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.98,0:00:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I know their crops have\Nbeen underperforming, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.12,0:00:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.06,0:00:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,They're HOARDING the\Nfood for themselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.69,0:00:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard the Mayor\Nof Appleoosa say
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.33,0:00:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,that if unicorns and\Npegasi want to eat,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.56,0:00:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,they can use their\NOWN hooves to dig.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.13,0:00:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,How awful!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.10,0:00:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We unicorns have to\Nstick together, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.31,0:00:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Chrysalis.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.35,0:00:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Another{\i0} successful\Nfield trip, I presume?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.72,0:00:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Spreading distrust among the\Nunicorns and earth ponies
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.82,0:00:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,is almost TOO easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.05,0:00:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,We could take down\NTwilight and her friends
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.92,0:00:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,a hundred times,\Nbut as long as
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.79,0:00:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,they have the "love" of\NEquestria behind them,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.36,0:01:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,they'd crawl back to\Ndefeat us. Not anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.23,0:01:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,No friendship,\Nno magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.63,0:01:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's SO obvious when\Nyou think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.97,0:01:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I did my part freaking\Nout the pegasi!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.37,0:01:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And Grogar's long absence\Nhas given ME time to prepare
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.11,0:01:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,the next part\Nof our plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.68,0:01:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Grogar's Bell!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.82,0:01:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,This artifact can steal\NANY creature's magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.39,0:01:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It holds that magic until\Nit is released by THIS spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.63,0:01:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Which means.. all the power\Ninside is OURS for the taking!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.03,0:01:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You're drooling\Non the bell.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.63,0:01:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's try the spell\N{\i1}before{\i0} Grogar gets back.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.37,0:01:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sick of waiting for that\Nold goat's "master plan."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.48,0:01:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Take my hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.28,0:01:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So we can all be\Npart of the spell!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.48,0:01:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Unless you'd prefer I\Ntake all the magic myself?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.89,0:02:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Our pact stands. What\Nwe do, we do together.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.62,0:02:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Once we defeat the\Nprotectors of Equestria,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.16,0:02:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,we can claim this land and rule\Nour kingdoms, ALONE once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.23,0:02:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.98,0:02:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.33,0:03:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Grogar: I have returned!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.73,0:03:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight Sparkle's\Ncoronation is today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.87,0:03:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And we are going to ruin\Nit with THIS artifact!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.00,0:03:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But to succeed, you\Nmust work together.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.21,0:03:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Chrysalis: Oh, way\Nahead of you, Grogar.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.45,0:03:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.62,0:03:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The Bell! You had it all this\Ntime!? Why didn't you tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.19,0:03:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,We're VILLIANS, duh.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.81,0:04:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ [comedic music] ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.81,0:04:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That was unexpected.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.92,0:04:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait. Discord\Nwas Grogar!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.69,0:04:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Like the whole time?\NShould we follow him..?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.13,0:04:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Without magic, he's no threat.\NBesides, WE have plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.30,0:04:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ [happy music] ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.10,0:04:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Celestia: Doesn't she look so\Nadorably regal up there?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.80,0:04:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Our little Twilight,\Nall grown up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.44,0:04:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Should we tell her that we've\Ncleared out our royal suites
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.01,0:04:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,so she and Spike can move in?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.71,0:04:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, maybe wait until\NAFTER the coronation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.65,0:04:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight doesn't\Nneed anything else
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.98,0:04:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,to worry about today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.38,0:04:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you freakin'\Nout yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.65,0:04:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.62,0:04:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I don't know. It's not\Nevery day the princesses
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.56,0:04:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,that have ruled Equestria\Nfor hundreds of moons
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.56,0:04:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,retire and pass all their\Nresponsibilities on to you
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.30,0:04:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,and your friends..
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.36,0:04:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, THAT. Actually, I'm\Nfeeling pretty good!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.97,0:05:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We've all faced so\Nmuch, and come out OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.90,0:05:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I know we're up\Nto the challenge
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.20,0:05:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,of keeping Equestria\Nsafe and happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.17,0:05:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing we\Ncan't handle together.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.21,0:05:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Which reminds me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.35,0:05:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Royal advisor?\NWhat's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.11,0:05:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,A new position I\Ncreated for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.42,0:05:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been\Nat my side
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.42,0:05:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,for every step\Nof this journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.55,0:05:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Knowing I had\Nyou to count on
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.82,0:05:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,gave me the\Nstrength I needed
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.96,0:05:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,to grow and succeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.12,0:05:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't be\Nhere without you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.19,0:05:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.36,0:05:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You know I'll always be\Nyour right-hoof dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.13,0:05:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I was hoping you'd say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.47,0:05:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Because now that my\Ncrown's been fitted,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.23,0:05:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,we have some royal\Nerrands to run!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.14,0:05:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.64,0:05:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're sure this is\Nwhere Pinkie told us to get
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.21,0:05:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,the blackberries for her\Nspecial coronation dessert?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.95,0:05:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe they keep their\Nproduce in the back?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.72,0:05:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope! This is\Nall we got.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.42,0:05:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But I got a special\Non these taters!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.79,0:05:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, no thank you.\NWe'll keep looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.52,0:05:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Blech!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.99,0:06:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh, Twilight, darling!\NYou're just in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.73,0:06:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Only one more\Npre-coronation stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.16,0:06:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,We're picking up\Nthe final touch
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.60,0:06:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,for your apres-hors\Nd'oevres gown.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.37,0:06:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that before or\Nafter the royal
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.84,0:06:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,marshmallow-eating\Ncontest gown?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.50,0:06:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What? I hadn't\Nmade one of those!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.57,0:06:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You must tell me when they\Nadd these sorts of things...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.54,0:06:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's OK, Rarity.\NI was just joking.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.78,0:06:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Joking? Day of\Nyour coronation?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.98,0:06:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You've come a long\Nway, Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.15,0:06:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.26,0:06:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's odd.\NThey LOOK open...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.63,0:06:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.56,0:06:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Well, this\Nbeing a thread shop,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.43,0:06:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I\Nmight buy some..?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.57,0:06:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Put the bits in\Nthe mail slot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.17,0:06:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What was\NTHAT about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.47,0:06:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You know designers. Don't\Nlike being interrupted
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.67,0:06:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,when they're on a\Ncreative roll!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.34,0:06:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,With thread this exquisite,\Ncan you blame them?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.85,0:06:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Rainbow Dash: Weather for the\Ncoronation is sunny skies!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.18,0:06:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It was weird, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.92,0:07:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Not many pegasi wanted to\Nhelp me clear the clouds.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.65,0:07:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,They were kinda\Non edge.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.09,0:07:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not the only ones..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.73,0:07:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the first shift in royal\Npower in over a millennium!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.83,0:07:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, everypony\Nis a little jumpy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.40,0:07:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Change does that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.43,0:07:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm sure it's not because\Nthey're worried about YOU.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.54,0:07:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,How could they be?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.31,0:07:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,HOW many times have you\Nsaved their flanks by now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.41,0:07:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right. I'll just\Nhave to let everypony know
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.94,0:07:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,that even with\NCelestia and Luna gone,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.85,0:07:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll make sure\Nthings stay the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.42,0:07:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight! There you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.46,0:07:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You mind tellin' your friend\Nhere that I don't need
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.62,0:07:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,an official guard\Nwherever I go?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.89,0:07:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Especially if he ain't\Ngonna help carry apples?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.20,0:07:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I appreciate you taking such\Ngood care of my friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.57,0:07:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,but we're fine now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.67,0:07:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the strangest thing. He\Nkept callin' me "Earth pony,"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.84,0:07:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,like I didn't have a name!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.47,0:07:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And watchin' me like he\Nthought I'd steal the silver!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.11,0:08:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Do NOT go in that kitchen!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.58,0:08:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You look like you\Nwere in a sugar war.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.58,0:08:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,For some reason,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.75,0:08:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,the bakers are SUPER\Ngrouchy with each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.35,0:08:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That unicorn chef started\Nthrowing dessert at Mrs. Cake!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.89,0:08:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I tried to help, but I got\Ncaught in the crossfire!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.53,0:08:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Tasty, tasty crossfire...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.30,0:08:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure this is just\Npre-coronation nerves?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.13,0:08:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Discord: Oh, my\Naching metatarsals!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.24,0:08:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Y'know, you forget how\Nconvenient snap-travel is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.64,0:08:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait. Did you just\NWALK here? On foot?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.85,0:08:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, actually. And I have\Na confession to make.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.28,0:08:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, I might have\Nmade the teeniest boo boo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.99,0:08:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,All very well-intentioned\Nand noble on my part, of course...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.76,0:08:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Get to the\Npoint, Discord.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.76,0:08:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You remember that whole\Nthing with King Sombra?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.80,0:08:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That was {\i1}slightly{\i0} my fault.\NAnd by slightly, I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.57,0:08:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I brought him back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.17,0:08:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You DID!? But why!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.50,0:08:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It seemed like a good\Nidea at the time!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.94,0:09:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Which is why I also brought\Nback three other villains
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.14,0:09:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,who are now on the loose...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.38,0:09:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,..And not really big\Nfans of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.48,0:09:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,So... my bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.46,0:09:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Luna: Let me get\Nthis straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.96,0:09:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You wanted to boost\NTwilight's confidence,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.09,0:09:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,so you brought back Chrysalis,\NCozy Glow, and Tirek
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.66,0:09:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,to attack her?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.90,0:09:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't forget Sombra!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.40,0:09:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And while you united\Nthese three villains,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.63,0:09:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,YOU pretended to be Grogar?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.24,0:09:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Discord! How could you do\Nthis to Twilight!? And us!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.34,0:09:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Look what a great job\Nyou did defeating Sombra!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.58,0:09:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,All the confidence\Nyou gained!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.85,0:09:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember the cheering?\NThe hoof bumps?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.98,0:09:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Except it was\Nall a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.95,0:09:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,A well-intentioned lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.09,0:09:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,For all the time\Nyou've spent with us,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.96,0:09:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,you really haven't picked\Nup too much in the way of
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.82,0:09:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,friendship lessons, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.43,0:09:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been setting\Nup challenges for us
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.06,0:09:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,the whole time,\Nhaven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.50,0:09:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,None of our successes\Nwere actually real!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.60,0:09:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course,\Nthey were!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.33,0:10:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You just had an {\i1}extremely{\i0}\Ngood-looking safety net.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.77,0:10:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike: And how was that\Nsupposed to HELP again?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.01,0:10:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I intended to prepare\NTwilight for anything
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.74,0:10:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,by orchestrating an epic\Nattack at her coronation.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.21,0:10:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You beastly beast!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.25,0:10:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you know how much\Nthis day means to Twilight!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.12,0:10:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,AND ME! I made her dress!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.25,0:10:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Why wait until now for\Nsuch a horrible plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.02,0:10:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't take a final exam\Non your first day of class!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.26,0:10:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Just think, after\Ndefeating THREE baddies,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.76,0:10:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight would\NHAVE to believe
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.03,0:10:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,that she's the leader\Nwe all know she is!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.43,0:10:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You have made a grave\Nmisjudgment, Discord..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.50,0:10:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have anything ELSE\Nyou would like to tell us?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.11,0:10:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like the good\Nnews or the bad news?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.11,0:10:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,THAT wasn't the bad news!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.15,0:10:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,All my chaos magic is... gone.\NTrapped in Grogar's bell.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.95,0:10:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,[sigh] So what's the good news?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.52,0:10:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Chrysalis, Tirek, and\NCozy Glow now have
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.36,0:11:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,all of the real\NGrogar's magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.59,0:11:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,In what WORLD is\Nthat GOOD NEWS!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.86,0:11:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Compared to me\Nlosing my powers,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.90,0:11:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,anything else\NIS good news.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.40,0:11:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight, Luna, we\Nneed to make a plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.07,0:11:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's not too late to stop\Nthis DISASTER from happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.84,0:11:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I need some\Ntime to think first.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.41,0:11:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, there isn't any time!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.18,0:11:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Look what I overheard\Nthem saying!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.95,0:11:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Just listen to my voice\Nand use your imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.85,0:11:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Let the fool go. Without\Nmagic, he's no threat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.69,0:11:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, we have plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.73,0:11:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The lame six are so\Nbusy being perfect,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.96,0:11:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,they haven't even noticed\Nwhat we've been up to!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.60,0:11:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Have I mentioned how\Ngreat revenge is?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.50,0:11:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you got a name picked\Nout for your future kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.61,0:11:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it's time to\Ndestroy Equestria!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.02,0:11:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,They're probably on their way\Nto attack Canterlot.. right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.82,0:12:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we'll stop 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.69,0:12:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,HOW? Stopping Sombra by\Nhimself was hard enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.16,0:12:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And that was with lord-of-\Nchaos training wheels!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.23,0:12:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight, it doesn't\Nmatter if Discord set up
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.20,0:12:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,your successes or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.13,0:12:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,WE believe in you..\Nand always have.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.77,0:12:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Lean on your strengths to\Ncounter your weaknesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.81,0:12:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,My strengths?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.74,0:12:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. Spike!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.51,0:12:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Send a letter to Starswirl.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.05,0:12:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell him we need the Pillars to\Nguard the border of Canterlot.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.78,0:12:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} If the villains are{\i0}\N{\i1} coming for a fight,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.55,0:12:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} we'll have one{\i0}\N{\i1} waiting for them.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.89,0:12:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} With Chrysalis on the loose,{\i0}\N{\i1} she'll go after Starlight.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.92,0:12:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Warn Cadance and{\i0}\N{\i1} Shining Armor.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.79,0:12:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} They're our final line{\i0}\N{\i1} of defense if we fail.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.33,0:12:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The ultimate battle for the\Nfate of Equestria...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.23,0:12:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,is coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.20,0:12:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not going anywhere\Nuntil you two STOP ARGUING!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.27,0:12:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Chrysalis, say something\Nnice about Tirek.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.88,0:12:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,GAH! He's...red.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.65,0:13:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Tirek...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.28,0:13:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,She's...not as\Nannoying as I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.52,0:13:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Good! Now we were talking\Nabout Grogar's Bell.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.29,0:13:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We should take the\Nmagic inside it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.52,0:13:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You know how\Npowerful Discord was.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.93,0:13:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That much chaos\Nmagic in OUR veins...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.66,0:13:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,But taking it ALL\Nwould be madness!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.20,0:13:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's impossible for any\Nother creature to control!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.47,0:13:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess if you need a\Nguinea pig to find out
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.84,0:13:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,if anypony can use chaos\Nmagic... I'll volunteer!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.85,0:13:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,FOOLS! Now I have more\Npower than ALL OF YOU!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.26,0:13:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Kneel before my might!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.44,0:13:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahh! Take it back! TAKE IT BACK!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.75,0:14:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Still think chaos\Nmagic is a good idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.12,0:14:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave it in the bell. We've\Ngot a kingdom to conquer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.85,0:14:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So, where should\Nwe strike first?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.39,0:14:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,[chuckle] {\i1}Everywhere{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.56,0:14:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.13,0:14:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,We've faced enemies\Nof Equestria before.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.73,0:14:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And we've ALWAYS succeeded.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.77,0:14:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That wouldn't be possible\Nwithout all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.37,0:14:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You're welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.47,0:14:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Dude. Read the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.07,0:14:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So I ask for your\Nhelp again today,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.01,0:14:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,in what is our\Nbiggest battle yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.14,0:14:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,ALL of Equestria is at stake,\Nand I can't do this alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.25,0:14:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm not afraid. Because\Nwith friendship as our armor,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.45,0:14:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,and teamwork as our power,\Nnopony can ever bring us down!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.52,0:14:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, COME ON.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.66,0:14:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Where'd you get that, a daily\Naffirmations calendar? Yeesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.36,0:14:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Cozy Glow!? You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.97,0:15:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,...about to wipe\Nthe floor with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.70,0:15:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, it's true! Alicorns\Nreally DO have more fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.65,0:15:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Starswirl: Spread out\Nand stay ready, friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.22,0:15:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Canterlot depends on us!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.18,0:15:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.42,0:15:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.31,0:15:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ [dramatic music] ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.15,0:15:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha ha ha ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.71,0:15:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.33,0:16:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Magic seasoned with\Nage. Delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.23,0:16:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.74,0:16:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.04,0:16:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, run along! The big\Nstallions are playing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.91,0:16:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Somnambula! Warn...\Nthe princesses....
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.47,0:16:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.26,0:16:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! The perfect dessert\Nto a LEGENDARY meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.41,0:16:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.54,0:16:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay with your\Nbuddy; no running.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.60,0:16:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Just follow\NCounselor Trixie.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.71,0:16:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Chrysalis: Starlight, starbright,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.07,0:16:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,where's the pony\NI want to FIGHT?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.98,0:16:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to go. You got this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.98,0:16:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Nopony does a great and\Npowerful escape like Trixie.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.65,0:17:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah. Just the headmare\NI want to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.49,0:17:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,YOU didn't make\Nan appointment.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.23,0:17:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this place!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.03,0:17:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Somewhere you\Ncan't hurt anypony.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.43,0:17:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Wrong. I can hurt YOU!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.45,0:17:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Agh! Stay still so I can blast you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.25,0:17:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah, real\Nmotivating.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.87,0:17:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.39,0:17:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll pay for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.73,0:17:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Put it on my {\i1}tab{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.52,0:17:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.98,0:18:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I'll have all eternity\Nto take my revenge on YOU!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.43,0:18:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Stand down{\i0}, Cozy Glow.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.00,0:18:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Gee, I guess I could. But...\NI'm having too much FUN!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.67,0:18:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready, sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.31,0:18:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! What are you..?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.32,0:18:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,NO!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.46,0:18:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the problem\Nwith you magic-types.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.13,0:18:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so reliant on\Nall your special power,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.86,0:18:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,you forget to use\Nyour BRAINS!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.13,0:18:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep telling yourself\Nthat. NOW!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.47,0:18:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,WHOA!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.94,0:19:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.21,0:19:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,SURPRISE ATTACK!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.48,0:19:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Fly my pretties!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.25,0:19:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.44,0:19:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Wah! Agh!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.96,0:19:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.36,0:19:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.81,0:19:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You think your pathetic\Nshield can stop us?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.75,0:19:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,[cackle] The Pillars have\Nbeen defeated.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.35,0:19:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Your school is abandoned. Face\Nit, Twilight. You've lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.16,0:19:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You can attack us\Nand we may fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.79,0:19:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,But Equestria will still\Nstand, united in friendship!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.30,0:19:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And we won't stop\Nuntil we defeat you,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.43,0:20:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,no matter how many\Nponies you take down!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.67,0:20:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you all notice\Nsomething was wrong
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.91,0:20:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,in Equestria?\NWe've been busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.81,0:20:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,A whisper here,\Na rumor there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.45,0:20:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Destroy some crops.\NCause some damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.18,0:20:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Turn pony against pony.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.72,0:20:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Until your whole\Nkingdom is on edge,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.29,0:20:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,waiting for just\None tiny thing
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.42,0:20:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,to push them\Nover the brink!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.29,0:20:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no backup friends or\Nrainbow magic to save you now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.00,0:20:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Golly, I think it's time\Nfor some REDECORATING!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.64,0:20:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what's stronger than\N{\i1}friendship{\i0}, Twilight? FEAR!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.01,0:20:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Because when you have\Nto protect yourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.02,0:20:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,you don't have time\Nfor anypony else!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.62,0:20:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Too bad you never\Ntaught THAT in school.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.95,0:20:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ [dramatic music] ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.42,0:20:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.03,0:21:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.66,0:21:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.97,0:21:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, Twilight. Get help!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.50,0:21:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll hold 'em\Ntill you get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.24,0:21:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,NO! I can't\Nleave you here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.27,0:21:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's our only chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.81,0:21:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll come up with\NSOMETHING to save the day!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.84,0:21:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You always do!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.35,0:21:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We believe in you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.52,0:21:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Fly, you foal!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.88,0:21:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ [intense music] ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.39,0:21:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
